  {name: "[神人] 板橋 The Toast Heaven", content: "\n\n<a href=\"http://imgur.com/Jy4tuoR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://imgur.com/Jy4tuoR</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/Jy4tuoR.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n小弟昨日在板橋文化路巷內的吐司天堂用餐\n\n被圖中這位馬尾氣質女店員深深的吸引\n\n他用溫柔的聲音幫我點餐 親切的服務\n\n讓我回味無窮\n\n他散發出的韻味有點像陳綺貞\n\n用餐時一直偷看他卻忘記偷偷拍下來\n\n只好在離開時從窗外拍他的身影\n\n雖然沒有正面照 但跪求各位大大幫神\n\n不要噓我\n\n\n\n--\n<span class=\"f2\"></span>", user_id: nil, avatar_file_name: nil, avatar_content_type: nil, avatar_file_size: nil, avatar_updated_at: nil, type_id: nil, cover_image: nil, ptt_post_id: "M.1451276699.A.669.html", ptt_post_link: "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Beauty/M.1451276699.A.669.html"},
