  {name: "[正妹] 萌蠢？霸氣？反差萌 - 中元すずか", content: "\n中元すずか（中元鈴香Nakamoto Suzuka），1997年生\n\n為什麼說中元すずか反差大呢？\n\n這得從她的演藝生涯開始說起。中元すずか的歌唱天賦很好，從小備受矚目，後來加入偶\n像團體櫻花學元，平時是個天然呆甚至有點蠢的女生，講起話會一口氣講一大串不停，很\n囉唆XD\n\n但是自從擔任BABYMETAL主唱之後，成為搖滾樂團的主唱，由於表演形式的關係，中元す\nずか沒有說話的機會（BABYMETAL的演唱會一口氣唱歌跳舞到結束），加上霸氣外露的歌\n聲，被外國人戲稱為Queen Su。\n\n平常憨傻會自己講話自己傻笑那種，可是站舞臺上馬上換一個人。\n\n以下照片就分開來排，感受一下差距～\n\n\n\n\n<span class=\"f3 hl\">平時\n</span>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y9y49W1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/Y9y49W1.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/Y9y49W1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>這大約是2012年的照片\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/vzJpGw7.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/vzJpGw7.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/vzJpGw7.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/rHAmwun.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/rHAmwun.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/rHAmwun.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>這張更年輕一點拍的\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/3sTiEic.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/3sTiEic.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/3sTiEic.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/hY1BC7q.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/hY1BC7q.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/hY1BC7q.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>幼兒肥時期\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/5lZ5vwM.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/5lZ5vwM.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/5lZ5vwM.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fKZVetp.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/fKZVetp.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/fKZVetp.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>就是個鄰家女孩\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/CHMTWHK.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/CHMTWHK.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/CHMTWHK.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/gz76xln.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/gz76xln.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/gz76xln.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/nGdGBGb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/nGdGBGb.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/nGdGBGb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/mm1cyMz.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/mm1cyMz.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/mm1cyMz.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>小時候可愛，長大後美麗\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/u3Ujbd4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/u3Ujbd4.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/u3Ujbd4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/5IZfPPA.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/5IZfPPA.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/5IZfPPA.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/u6eWofb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/u6eWofb.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/u6eWofb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n<span class=\"f3 hl\">上臺\n</span><span class=\"f3 hl\">\n</span><a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/LZKzLGP.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"f3 hl\">http://i.imgur.com/LZKzLGP.jpg</span></a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/LZKzLGP.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>收起笑容，整個人不一樣了<span class=\"f3 hl\">\n</span><span class=\"f3 hl\">\n</span><a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/0jx3fdo.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"f3 hl\">http://i.imgur.com/0jx3fdo.jpg</span></a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/0jx3fdo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<span class=\"f3 hl\">\n</span><a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/9k6tW1W.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"f3 hl\">http://i.imgur.com/9k6tW1W.jpg</span></a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\