  {name: "Re: [神人] 地產記者徐微欣", content: "\n<span class=\"f2\">※ 引述《meianhua (我是男生唷)》之銘言：\n</span><span class=\"f6\">: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/K0aFQlBn1gY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/K0aFQlBn1gY</a>\n</span><div class=\"richcontent\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"385\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/K0aFQlBn1gY\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div>\n<span class=\"f6\">: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/KfxL1wBefvU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/KfxL1wBefvU</a>\n</span><div class=\"richcontent\"><iframe class=\"youtube-player\" type=\"text/html\" width=\"640\" height=\"385\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/KfxL1wBefvU\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div>\n<span class=\"f6\">: <a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/BK5bNyw.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/BK5bNyw.jpg</a>\n</span><div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/BK5bNyw.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<span class=\"f6\">: 如題 一個臉蛋甜美身材豐腴聲音超嗲的女記者\n</span><span class=\"f6\">: 剛在非凡新聞看到 以前好像都在蘋果出現\n</span><span class=\"f6\">: 記得之前有一次在蘋果看到她介紹地產美女 結果論臉蛋她簡直樂勝啊 滿喜歡這種肩膀寬\n</span><span class=\"f6\">: 肉肉的女生 帶股誘惑的性感 可惜網路上照片都谷歌不到\n</span><span class=\"f6\">: 有神人可以神她的社群網站或照片的嗎？感謝 ≧▽≦\n</span>\n今天看總統辯論會有看到\n\n跳到TVBS新聞當記者了\n\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/OnPnb2j.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/OnPnb2j.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/OnPnb2j.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/weGPwR2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://i.imgur.com/weGPwR2.jpg</a>\n<div class=\"richcontent\"><img src=\"//i.imgur.com/weGPwR2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n\n--\n<span class=\"f2\"></span>", user_id: nil, avatar_file_name: nil, avatar_content_type: nil, avatar_file_size: nil, avatar_updated_at: nil, type_id: nil, cover_image: "http://i.imgur.com/weGPwR2.jpg", ptt_post_id: "M.1451233551.A.C2F.html", ptt_post_link: "https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Beauty/M.1451233551.A.C2F.html"},
